<DocsPageTitle Path="Migration">
    Blazorise 2.0 Migration CLI
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Blazorise.Migrator is a command-line tool that scans your solution or project and helps you move to Blazorise 2.0.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    Use <Code>analyze</Code> to generate a report in dry-run mode, then use <Code>migrate</Code> to apply changes when you are ready.
</DocsPageParagraph>

